<D>__{jane.}
<A>__{jane pulls him inside. she falls into his arms. they embrace passionately. jane is actively pulling him towards her, delirious with love and longing.}
<T>__{cut to:}
<A>__{the exact same shot of jane opening the door. st john rivers is there, having waded through the drifting snow.}
<C>__{jane}
<D>__{mr st john what on earth brings you away from your hearth on a night like this? has anything happened? there's no bad news i hope?}
<C>__{st john}
<D>__{how easily alarmed you are.}
