<C>__{st john }
<D>__{well, since you won't ask the governess's name, i must tell you. i have it written down here in black and white.}
<A>__{he hands her the paper. on it are doodled the heads of some of her pupils. she has absently written jane eyre in the margin several times.}
<C>__{st john }
<D>__{a solicitor named briggs wrote to me of a jane eyre. i knew a jane elliott. this paper resolved my suspicion into certainty.}
